                        <interp inst="t18631026-name-396" type="given" value="JOHN ANTONY"></interp>JOHN ANTONY NICHOLSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a shopman to the prosecutor—I received information from Hammond, went out, and saw the prisoner and another woman standing opposite the window, three yards from the door—I passed</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186310260088"></xptr>
               <p>behind them, lifted the prisoner's shawl, took this piece of stuff from under her arm, and asked her where it was found—she made no answer—it is my master's property—it was impossible for any person to take it from the pile without assistance.</p>
